item.title: About Me
item.description: Hey! My name’s Luke. I’m a 26 year old Tech Manager, with experience in data, financial and systems analysis. I was born and raised in Brisbane, Australia, and grew up with an interest in IT and Finance. I studied Bachelor Degrees in Computer Science and Business, and went on to do a Masters Degree in Applied Finance. Now, I’m working on building my career, my experiences, my wealth and my happiness.
